item.title: A comparison between PMBM Bayesian track initiation and labelled RFS adaptive birth
item.description: This paper provides a comparative analysis between the adaptive birth model used in the labelled random finite set literature and the track initiation in the Poisson multi-Bernoulli mixture (PMBM) filter, with point-target models.

item.title: Symmetry-Aware Transformer-based Mirror Detection
